# React / UI Rules

## Components
- Pages: `src/presentation/features/{feature}/`
- Layout: `src/presentation/components/layout/`
- UI primitives: `src/presentation/components/ui/` (shadcn)

## Pattern
```tsx
'use client'
import { useApp } from '@/application/providers/app-provider'

export function MyPage() {
  const { t } = useApp()
  return <h1>{t('page_title')}</h1>
}
```

## Navigation
- Use Next.js App Router: `useRouter()` + `PATHS` from `@/domain/constants/routes`
- Do not add footer inside landing features (global Footer exists)

## Style
- Tokens: `src/presentation/styles/tokens.css`
- Container: `container-responsive`
- Card: shadcn `Card`

## Forms
- Input: shadcn `Input`
- Select on auth: `className="select-auth"`
- Errors: i18n keys (`error_required`, ...)

## Do not
- Hardcode English/Uzbek text
- Use `$` for currency
- Import from `@/components/*` or `@/lib/*`

Docs: `docs/UI_UX_GUIDELINES.md`, `docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`
